data.description: Secluded oasis in the heart of Denver.  Escape the bustle without leaving the city!  Beautiful, meticulously maintained, move in ready ranch style home tucked away on almost 2 acres of land.  Gather everyone comfortably in the open concept living space.  Splash into summer fun in the sparkling new above-ground pool with new deck!  Stainless steel fridge, granite countertops, and laminate wood flooring in kitchen, dining room and entranceway.  Granite countertops and double sink vanity with walk-in shower, deep tub and walk-in closet in master bath.  Great yard for kids and/or entertaining.  Sit out on the front porch and watch the kids swing and play in the expansive yard. Well built tree house out back, go cart and white cabinet in bathroom convey with home!  8x8 storage shed and 2-car carport.  New HVAC in 2020, new water heater in 2023.  Schedule your showing today, and step into your dream home.
